Don DOROTHY and Pacific Northern Airlines, Inc., a corporation, Appellants, v. C. A. McCANDLESS, Appellee. No. 12230. United States Court of Appeals Ninth Circuit May 1, 1950. John E. Manders and Edward V. Davis, Anchorage, Alaska, for appellants. W. N. Cuddy, Wendell P. Kay, Anchorage, Alaska, for appellee.

Before MATHEWS, STEPHENS and OR'R, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The judgment of the District Court is affirmed.
